<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/styles/base.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/styles/layout.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/styles/header.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .card {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 80px auto;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        li {
            margin-left: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .github-card {
            text-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 30px auto 0 auto;
            padding: 25px 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: #45626b;
            color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.377), inset 0 0 32px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.747);
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
            text-align: center;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px black;
            position: relative;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .github-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0px 5px 14px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.562), inset 0 0 32px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.747);
        }

        .github-card h3 {
            margin: 10px 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .github-card h3 img {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            filter: brightness(0) invert(1) drop-shadow(1px 1px 2px black);
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px black;
        }

        .github-card a {
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 500;
            word-break: break-all;
            text-decoration: underline;
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
        }

        .github-card a:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .github-card::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            z-index: 0;
            background: url('https://raw.githubusercontent.com/cloudsucker/pleo/main/static/logo.png') center center / 140% no-repeat;
            filter: blur(1px);
            opacity: 0.6;
            border-radius: 12px;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .github-card>* {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    {{ header_fragment }}

    <div class="card">
        <h1><b>Welcome to PLEO</b></h1>
        <p><b>PLEO</b> is a minimalistic social network implemented on <b>FastAPI</b> with support for:</p>
        <ul style="margin-top:0; margin-bottom:1em;">
            <li>Registration and authorization</li>
            <li>Publishing posts</li>
            <li>User profiles</li>
            <li>Feeds (<a href="/wall/">The Wall</a>)</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="github-card">
            <a href="https://github.com/cloudsucker/pleo" target="_blank"
                style="display:block;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
                <h3>
                    <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/25/25231.png" alt="GitHub logo">
                    GitHub
                </h3>
                <div style="font-size:1.05em;word-break:break-all;">github.com/cloudsucker/pleo</div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>